casebody.data:
May 1, 2002

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2001- 1693. Spalding v. Coulson.

Cuyahoga App. No. 76666. On response to show cause order and on response to show cause order of Robert Coulson. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C. J., Resnick, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. Douglas, J., dissents. F.E. Sweeney, J., dissents and would refer this cause to mediation.
